A 50 year old man has been arrested on Monday for the assault of his 49 year old wife who is two months pregnant in Katlehong.Provincial spokesperson Captain Kay Makhubela said the cause of the attack is yet unknown however the police do know that the couple is separated and the women is living with a different man.&#8220;The man will be appearing in court in the next 48 hours,&#8221; said Makhubela.The suspect is being charged with assault and domestic violence.Police are still investigating the case.-TNA Reporter